<td class="author-text">Ng, C., Ernst, T., Paik, E., and M. Bagnulo, &ldquo;<a href="http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-nemo-multihoming-issues-04.txt">Analysis of Multihoming in Network Mobility Support</a>,&rdquo; draft-ietf-nemo-multihoming-issues-04 (work in progress), October&nbsp;2005.</td></tr>
