<a name="rfc.section.A"></a><h3>Appendix A.&nbsp;Change Log From Previous Version</h3>

<p></p>
<ul class="text">
<li>Moved "Scenarios" up into a "Motivations" section
</li>
<li>Added tables to summarizes goals with respect and issues
</li>
<li>Goal "Increased Bandwidth" replaced with "Aggregated Bandwidth"
</li>
<li>Goal "Redundancy/Fault-Recovery replaced with "Reliability"
</li>
<li>Goal "Bicasting" merged with "Reliability"
</li>
<li>Added issue "Change of Traffic Characteristics "
</li>
<li>Added "Conclusion"
</li>
<li>Minor update everywhere to fit the above mentioned changes
</li>
</ul>

